welcome_message_body: "Welcome to scenic Lake Stickney! This charming city is known for its beautiful lake, friendly locals, and relaxing atmosphere. We invite you to explore and experience all that Lake Stickney has to offer during your stay."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport serves all commercial flights and provides a range of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport caters to private and charter flights and offers a comfortable and convenient experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport serves as the hub for all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Seaplane Terminal
terminals.description: The seaplane terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport is used for all seaplane flights, providing easy access to the surrounding islands and waterways.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all commercial flights at Boeing Field/King County International Airport.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is primarily used for general aviation and cargo flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network throughout the terminals.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
